  "abstract": "Resistance to rust (Puminia arachidis Speg.) and late leafspot\r\n(Cercospridium personaturn (Berk. & Curt.) Deighton) in some\r\npeanut genotypes was studied under field conditions. Late\r\nleafspot development was also assessed in the glasshbuse and the\r\nparameters lesion diameter, defoliation percentage and sporulation\r\ngave highly significant correlations with the field disease\r\nscores. Several genotypes were found to be resistant to both rust\r\nand late leafspot and should be useful sources of multiple diseaseresistance\r\nin a breeding program.",
